"{\"uid\": \"dailycaller.com-2024-08-01-olympics-triathlon-seine-dirty-water-comments\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"(Photo by David Goldman / POOL / AFP) (Photo by DAVID GOLDMAN/POOL/AFP via Getty Images)  Belgian Olympic triathlete Jolien Vermeylen appeared horrified after being forced to compete in the filthy waters of the River Seine during the 2024 games Wednesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_P._Goldman\", \"score\": 0.999998562366851, \"rank\": 1.4374528994283972e-06, \"text\": \"David Goldman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_P._Goldman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_P._Goldman\"}, {\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 36, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999999290594, \"rank\": 6.119655386110679e-11, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 48, \"end\": 61, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_P._Goldman\", \"score\": 0.999998562366851, \"rank\": 1.4374528994283972e-06, \"text\": \"DAVID GOLDMAN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_P._Goldman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_P._Goldman\"}, {\"begin\": 67, \"end\": 70, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999999290594, \"rank\": 6.119655386110679e-11, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 80, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999945808905474, \"rank\": 4.4634931898228886e-06, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 90, \"end\": 97, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9999981788017279, \"rank\": 1.821013504602815e-06, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 211, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite spending$1.5 billionand working for months to try and clean the Seine, officials at theOlympicswere forced to postpone the triathlon until water quality testing revealed acceptable levels of grossness.\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 329, \"end\": 334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999998258318, \"rank\": 1.739034337271393e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Wednesday, the waters were considered clean enough for the competition.\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But one athlete says she \\\"felt and saw things\\\" she does not \\\"want to think about\\\" while swimming in the river,accordingto Metro.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I drank a lot of water, so we will know tomorrow if I am sick or not,\\\" Vermeylen told a local news outlet.\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 779, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It does not taste like Coca-Cola or Sprite, of course.\\\"\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 836, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics Opening Ceremony Goes Viral Because Everyone Is Like 'WTF Even Is This?\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'https://t.co/NuwNyYy4ql  - SMD (@smdowner)July 27, 2024    \\\"While swimming under the bridge, I felt and saw things that we should not think about too much,\\\" she continued.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Seine has been dirty for a hundred years, so they can not say that the safety of the athletes is a priority.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1096, \"end\": 1101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999998258318, \"rank\": 1.739034337271393e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's bulls***!\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(RELATED: 'Malicious Acts' Wreak Havoc At Olympics)  Vermeylen says she took precautions to avoid getting sick from the water.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She unfortunately ended up drinking a fair amount of it during the competition.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If the race had not taken place, it would have been a disgrace for the organisation, for Paris, for France,\\\" she noted.\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1519, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.3617693341774303e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999502386561705, \"rank\": 4.916228423918951e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was now or never, and they could not cancel the race completely either.\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now they just have to hope that there will not be too many sick athletes.\\\"\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I took pro-biotics, I drank my Yakult, I could not do more.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1762, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had the idea of \\u200b\\u200bnot drinking water, but yes, it failed,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes dive into the Seine river to start the swimming stage of the men's individual triathlon at the Paris 2024 Olympic Games in central Paris on July 31, 2024.\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999998258318, \"rank\": 1.739034337271393e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 1975, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.3617693341774303e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo by David Goldman / POOL / AFP) (Photo by DAVID GOLDMAN/POOL/AFP via Getty Images)  Athletes swim in the Seine river for the triathlon event at the Olympic Games in Paris, July 31, 2024.Natation des athletes dans la Seine pour l epreuve du triathlon masculin des jeux olympiques a Paris, le 31 juillet 2024.\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2009, \"end\": 2022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_P._Goldman\", \"score\": 0.999998562366851, \"rank\"