text\": \"Lucas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lucas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lucas\"}, {\"begin\": 2359, \"end\": 2364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lucas\", \"score\": 0.8208191422464465, \"rank\": 0.209481653410655, \"text\": \"Lucas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lucas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lucas\"}, {\"begin\": 2369, \"end\": 2372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999999290594, \"rank\": 6.119655386110679e-11, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 2415, \"end\": 2420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999945808905474, \"rank\": 4.4634931898228886e-06, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite knowing of the utterly repugnant conditions of the Seine River for the last century, it is kind of shocking thatOlympic officialswent ahead with the race instead of finding a better alternative.\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How lazy and egotistical do you have to be to do something like that?\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(RELATED: Video Shows Brazilian Olympian Expressing Her Love For Jesus While Winning Medal)  I am not much of an athlete but I have heard they are very into health and fitness.\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If this is the case, why did they agree to put their bodies in a potentially deadly body of water?\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For a medal?\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Really?\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Have we gotten so flipping stupid as a species that we are forcing the world's top athletes to risk theirphysical healthto win a piece of metal?\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To me, this poses the age-old question: would you jump off a cliff if everyone else was doing it?\", \"from\": 3225, \"to\": 3322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Guys, we have got to ask ourselves where our priorities are, because I do not think this type ofstupidbehavior is sustainable.\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TRENDING  \\u00a92025 The Daily Caller, Inc.\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Daily Caller | 1775 Eye Street NW | Suite 1150-290 | Washington, DC 20006\", \"from\": 3492, \"to\": 3569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3549, \"end\": 3563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Union_Station\", \"score\": 0.8101868931345004, \"rank\": 0.2342831105755352, \"text\": \"Washington, DC\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Union_Station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Union_Station\"}]}]}"